&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT’S AN ASSOCIATE DESIGN DIRECTOR AT HOOK?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hook is seeking a hands-on Associate Design Director to join one of our west coast teams.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
